title: Taking Baby Steps Toward Your Goals
itunes:title: Taking Baby Steps Toward Your Goal
description:
Get the Free Course here:
https://phit.click/freecourse

  

In this "best of" podcast, I talk about how you stay out of wanting to change everything at once and taking baby steps toward your weightloss goal. Making small changes has a lot more staying power than trying to change the world all at once.
